# 8. Recursion Tree / DP Table / Diagram

No recursion. No DP. Just a greedy walk.

```text
Original

100
1
1000

↓ rearrange

1
100
1000

↓ decrease

1
2
3

↓

Maximum = 3
```

Bucket-counting version of the same idea — instead of one element at a time, we sweep one **value level** at a time:

```text
value level :   1        2        3
count       :   1        0        2
prev before :   -        1        1
prev after  :   1        1        3   <- min(prev+count, value)
```

